704
00:32:29,490 --> 00:32:29,890
Okay.

705
00:32:35,490 --> 00:32:36,690
I'll take you to meet our supervisor.

706
00:32:36,910 --> 00:32:37,930
Mr. Wu is nice.

707
00:32:45,830 --> 00:32:46,350
Come in.

708
00:32:46,990 --> 00:32:47,370
Mr. Wu,

709
00:32:47,690 --> 00:32:48,670
