780
00:35:17,530 --> 00:35:18,510
to a welcome dinner.

781
00:35:19,930 --> 00:35:20,970
Then I won't stand on ceremony.

782
00:35:21,390 --> 00:35:22,050
I don't know

783
00:35:22,110 --> 00:35:23,070
